text: Johanna "Hanni" Hölzner (February 17, 1913 - 1988) was a German breaststroke swimmer who competed in the 1936 Summer Olympics. In 1936 she finished fourth in the 200 metre breaststroke event. ==External links== *Hanni Hölzner's profile at Sports Reference.com *Biography of Hanni Hölzner Category:1913 births Category:1988 deaths Category:German female swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of Germany Category:Swimmers at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:European Aquatics Championships medalists in swimming
